---
title: Thai Red Chicken Curry with Jasmine Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: Enjoy the medley of fragrant flavours in this red curry with a gentle warming heat. With garlic bringing an enticing aroma and crushed peanuts for addictive crunch, this is an easy way to enjoy a taste of
Thailand at home.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-red-chicken-curry-169c47f8.jpg
